These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, cola
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, electronic, hip-hop
1. the fan of electronic is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the fan of hip-hop and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | cola | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | funk    | hip-hop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, photography, gardening
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, software-developer, journalist
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the journalist is between the police-officer and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | cooking    | gardening        | photography |
| Job     | software-developer | journalist | police-officer         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, lemonade
3 different pets are kept: frog, horse, lizard
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking water is between the owner of the horse and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | water     | lemonade |
| Pet        | horse  | lizard | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, rock, house
3 different pets are kept: horse, frog, chinchilla
1. the fan of punk is the owner of the horse##1
2. the fan of house is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the horse##2
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | house     | punk |
| Pet           | frog | chinchilla | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, chess, hiking
3 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, dog
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | chess | hiking     | card-games |
| Pet     | dog    | cat | mouse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: german, argentine, indonesian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, sailing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is cricket is between the indonesian and the german##2
2. the german is the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | german  | argentine   | indonesian        |
| Sport         | sailing | cricket | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, lime, plum
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, polish, nigerian
1. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the russian is between the person eating plum and the polish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | lime  | lemon  | plum |
| Nationality   | polish | russian | nigerian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, superhero, time-travel
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, pakistani, egyptian
1. the person watching superhero movies is the egyptian##1
2. the pakistani is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | spy  | superhero  |
| Nationality   | polish | pakistani | egyptian |

