.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, golf, rowing
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, boat, car
1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | rowing | tennis | golf  |
| Transport   | car    | subway        | boat |

