.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, sprite
There 3 different types of food: orange, cabbage, artichoke
1. the person eating artichoke is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating orange##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | lemonade      | sprite      |
| Food       | cabbage  | artichoke | orange |

