The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, rugby
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
3. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | country   | classical   |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rugby | baseball |

