.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, funk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the fan of metal##2
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | juice | lemonade   | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | hip-hop | metal   |

 